[package]
name = "pallet-subtensor"

[dependencies.frame-support]

version = "4.0.0-dev"

branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"

version = "0.15.0"

git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"

version = "2.1.1"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.132"
features = ["derive"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde-tuple-vec-map]
version = "1.0.1"
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde_bytes]
version = "0.11.8"
features = ["alloc"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.serde_with]
version = "=2.0.0"
features = ["macros"]
default-features = false

[dependencies.sp-core]
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
default-features = false

[dependencies.sp-io]
version = "7.0.0"
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate.git"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"

[dependencies.sp-runtime]
version = "7.0.0"
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate.git"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
default-features = false

[dependencies.sp-std]
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
default-features = false

[dependencies.substrate-fixed]
git = "https://github.com/encointer/substrate-fixed.git"
tag = "v0.5.9"

[dev-dependencies]
rand = "0.8"

[dev-dependencies.pallet-balances]
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
features = ["std"]
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.parity-util-mem]
version = "0.11.0"
features = ["primitive-types"]

[dev-dependencies.sp-core]
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.sp-tracing]
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
default-features = false

[dev-dependencies.sp-version]
git = "https://github.com/paritytech/substrate"
branch = "polkadot-v0.9.39"
default-features = false

[features]
default = ["std"]
runtime-benchmarks = ["frame-benchmarking/runtime-benchmarks"]
std = ["codec/std", "frame-benchmarking/std", "frame-support/std", "frame-system/std", "scale-info/std"]
try-runtime = ["frame-support/try-runtime"]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
name = "pallet_subtensor"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
